This is a WikiForge-managed LLM Wiki. This wiki is NOT RAG ‚Äî sources are not chunked for retrieval. Instead, the LLM **incrementally builds and maintains a persistent wiki** ‚Äî a structured, interlinked collection of markdown files compiled from raw sources. When a new source is added, the LLM reads it, extracts key information, and integrates it into the existing wiki ‚Äî updating entity pages, revising topic summaries, noting contradictions, strengthening the evolving synthesis.

**The wiki is a compounding artifact.** The cross-references are already built. The contradictions are already flagged. The synthesis already reflects everything ingested. Every source makes the wiki richer; every query can compound back into it. The human curates sources and asks the right questions. The LLM does all the bookkeeping ‚Äî summarizing, cross-referencing, filing, and maintaining ‚Äî that makes a knowledge base actually useful over time.

